// QWERTY - MacOS Optimized
// | NONE |  Q  |  W  |  E  |  R  |  T  |   |  Y  |  U  |  I  |  O  |  P  | NONE |
// | NONE | CMD | ALT | SHFT| CTRL|  G  |   |  H  | CTRL| SHFT| ALT | CMD | NONE |
// | NONE |  Z  |  X  |  C  |  V  |  B  |   |  N  |  M  |  ,  |  .  |  -  | NONE |

// NAV - MacOS (Command/GUI Based)
// | NONE | ESC | F5  |CMD-F5|CMD-.|     |   |     | HOME|  UP | END | PGUP| NONE |
// | NONE | ALT | SHFT| CTRL| CMD |     |   |     | LFT | DWN | RGT | PGDN| NONE |
// | NONE |CMD-Z|CMD-X|CMD-C|CMD-V|     |   | INS |C-LFT|     |C-RGT|     | NONE |

// SYM - Paired Delimiters
// | NONE |  ¿  |  ?  |  ¡  |  !  |  \  |   |  |  |  (  |  )  |  <  |  >  | NONE |
// | NONE |  `  |  ~  |  "  |  '  |  &  |   |  @  |  {  |  }  |  [  |  ]  | NONE |
// | NONE |  ^  |  %  |  #  |  $  |  €  |   |  * |  +  |  =  |  -  |  /  | NONE |